OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778497376
OL,3,CLincoln City fans flood the streets
OL,4,Cfor promotion bus parade
OL,6,FThousands of Lincoln City fans have
OL,7,Flined the city's streets to celebrate
OL,8,Fthe club's historic promotion to the
OL,9,FChampionship for the first time in 65
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FThe Imps toured the city in an open-
OL,13,Ftop bus on Saturday after being
OL,14,Fcrowned League One Champions and
OL,15,Fearning a place in the second division.
OL,17,FDespite having one of the lowest
OL,18,Fbudgets in the league, Lincoln smashed
OL,19,Fexpectations by securing promotion in
OL,20,Fearly April.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
