FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778497376
OL,3,CLincoln City fans flood the streets
OL,4,Cfor promotion bus parade
OL,6,FSupporters transformed Lincoln city
OL,7,Fcentre into a sea of red and white to
OL,8,Fapplaud a landmark season.
OL,10,FOne fan said: "It's been amazing this
OL,11,Fyear. Couldn't have gone better
OL,12,Freally."
OL,14,F"I hope we get promoted to the Premier
OL,15,FLeague next season. That's what it's
OL,16,Fall about!", said another.
OL,18,FOnly nine years ago the club was in a
OL,19,Fnon-League position, and its success
OL,20,Fthis season has been widely praised as
OL,21,Fa product of a steady and organic rise.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778497376
OL,3,CLincoln City fans flood the streets
OL,4,Cfor promotion bus parade
OL,6,FMichael Skubala's side had a record-
OL,7,Fbreaking April. Landing the title,
OL,8,Fpromotion and earning 16 points from
OL,9,F18 available.
OL,11,FIt was a 2-1 win at Reading that
OL,12,Fensured the Imps return to the second
OL,13,Fdivision on Easter Monday, before
OL,14,Fwrapping up the title at Doncaster
OL,15,FRovers.
OL,17,FLincoln City Captain, Tendayi Darikwa,
OL,18,Fsaid: "We've always had a belief that
OL,19,Fwe have the capabilities in this squad
OL,20,Fto do something special.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778497376
OL,3,CLincoln City fans flood the streets
OL,4,Cfor promotion bus parade
OL,6,F"But probably around the turn of the
OL,7,Fnew year, after the results we went
OL,8,Fand got, we started to have a real
OL,9,Fbelief and inner feeling that we were
OL,10,Fgoing to achieve something.
OL,12,F"We've earned our right to be in the
OL,13,FChampionship and I'm sure there'll be
OL,14,Fsome special games next season with
OL,15,Fsome very big football clubs up and
OL,16,Fdown the country.
OL,18,F"But we believe in ourselves and I'm
OL,19,Fsure there'll be a few additions over
OL,20,Fthe summer to come and help us on our
OL,21,Fjourney as well."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778497376
OL,3,CLincoln City fans flood the streets
OL,4,Cfor promotion bus parade
OL,6,FSkubala said his squad and the fans
OL,7,Fdeserve to have pride in their club.
OL,9,FHe said: "I think it's been a
OL,10,Fhistorical season, the lads have been
OL,11,Fsensational this year. Getting
OL,12,Fpromoted for the first time in 65
OL,13,Fyears, 103 points - what a season.
OL,15,F"Today is about celebrating it with
OL,16,Fthe fans and celebrating with the
OL,17,Fcity. The lads have made the city
OL,18,Fproud and today is about enjoying it
OL,19,Ftogether.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
